alot of people judge this game because it seems like its about cooking when its really about remembering patters and quick reflexes. it also has its own kind of humor, which i personnaly really enjoy. 
if you have the chance to get it on sale i would definitly recommend you to buy this because its alot of fun but its also worth its full prize (:

btw: fk soup, that s**t is way to difficult D:

